Makes fun of angry people on Twitter. (brazilians only)

Create an app:

1. Setup your own app on Twitter at this URL twitter.com/apps/new
2. Choose ‘Client’ as the app type
3. Choose ‘Read & Write’ access unless you don’t need to send tweets.
4. Take the consumer key/consumer secret values.

Run the bot:

1. gem install chatterbot
2. ruby ragebot.rb
3. Enter the consumer key/consumer secret values when prompted.
4. Have fun!